  "description": "This project demonstrates a professional-grade **plugin-style CI integration** of: - ✅ Cypress for end-to-end testing - 🐞 Jira API for auto bug reporting - ⚙️ Jenkins (or GitHub Actions) for CI/CD automation",
  "main": "index.js",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node api/index.js",
    "test": "jest",
